data.description: Charming 5 bedroom, 3 full bath home located in Downtown Mckinney! Make yourself right at home with this well thought out floorpan with soaring ceilings and large windows offering lots of natural lighting. Prepare meals in the kitchen boasting lots of countertop space, double oven stove, cabinet space and a breakfast bar. Unwind in the spacious master suite featuring a garden tub, dual sinks and large walk-in closet with built-in shelves. Two of the secondary four bedrooms are located on the first floor. Make lasting memories upstairs in the spacious game room or spend time outdoors in the private backyard offering a beautiful gazebo, perfect for sitting out by a fire pit and enjoying great conversations with friend and family. MCKINNEY ISD and NO HOA! ASSUMABLE LOAN OPTION AT 2.75%!!
